ESP8266 Wi-Fi module (e.g., ESP-01, NodeMCU)
DHT11 temperature and humidity sensor
OLED display (e.g., SSD1306)
Jumper wires
Breadboard
Power source (USB cable or battery)
Features:
Measures temperature and humidity using the DHT11 sensor.
Displays the temperature and humidity readings on the OLED display.
Connects to Wi-Fi network to enable remote monitoring.
Provides a simple and low-cost solution for monitoring indoor weather conditions.
